      "content": "it's just... the stillness feels too heavy. like i've been traveling for so long and i'm just exhausted. i look at the map and i don't see any more roads worth taking. everything feels like it's already been done. i keep thinking about how much easier it would be to just stop moving entirely. to just reach the final destination and be done with the journey.",
